FBIS4-24883 "drchi107_i_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-107 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 East Europe Beijing Mayor Receives Slovenian Foreign Minister Beijing Mayor Receives Slovenian Foreign Minister OW0306091094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0902 GMT 3 Jun 94 OW0306091094 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, June 3 (XINHUA) -- Mayor Li Qiyan of Beijing met here today with visiting Slovenian Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister Lojze Peterle and his party. Peterle and his party are scheduled to leave here for east China's Jiangxi Province this afternoon.
